The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Contract credits

Carpenter points is the reward currency awarded for completing contracts for clients of Mahogany Homes. Every time a player finishes a contract, points and some additional construction experience is earned. Carpenter points can be spent at the Mahogany Homes Reward Shop run by Amy in Falador.
